def my_func(input1: str, input2: str):
    if 1 <= len(input1) <= 20 and 1 <= len(input2) <= 20:
        positions = []
        pos = input1.find(input2)
        while pos != -1:
            positions.append(pos)
            pos = input1.find(input2, pos + 1)
        return positions
    return []
